<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <title>Trakkor <%= (html_title = yield :html_title) ? html_title : '&mdash; Change tracking for web pages, no-frills.' %></title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'trakkor' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'base' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'themes/blue/style' %>

  <%= javascript_include_tag 'http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.4/jquery.min.js' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery.timeago.js' %>

  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="<%= image_path('favicon.ico') %>" />

  <% if controller.action_name == 'index' %>
  <link rel="commands" href="http://gist.github.com/9767.txt" />
  <% end %>

  <% if @tracker %>
  <link rel="alternate" type="application/atom+xml" href="<%= "#{url_for(@tracker)}.atom" %>" />
  <link rel="microsummary" type="text/plain" href="<%= "#{url_for(@tracker)}.microsummary" %>" />
  <% end %>

</head>
<body>
  <div id="container">
    <div id="header">
      <h1><a href="/">Trakkor</a></h1>

      <div id="main-navigation">
        <ul>
          <li class="first active"><a href="/">Introduction</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="wrapper">
      <div id="main">

        <div class="block" id="block-text">
          <div class="content">
            <div class="inner">

                <%= yield  %>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="footer">
          <div class="block">
            <p><a href='<%= root_path %>'>Trakkor</a>, tracking your changes since May 2008.
                Running on <a href='http://rubyonrails.org'>Rails</a>.
                Created by <a href='http://better-idea.org'>Matthias LÃ¼dtke</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

  <% if controller.action_name == 'index' %>
      <div id="sidebar">
        <div class="block">
          <h3>Ubiquity integration</h3>
          <div class="content">
          <p>As Firefox user you might want to try this  <a href='http://gist.github.com/9767' title="Trakkor's Ubiquity command on GitHub">Ubiquity command</a>.</p>
          <p>The command allows you to create Trakkors by selecting text on a web page.</p>
          <p>To use the command, install <a href='https://wiki.mozilla.org/Labs/Ubiquity' title='Ubiquity project on mozilla.org'>the latest Ubiquity</a> and come back here to subscribe to the Trakkor Command.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
  <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>

<a href="http://github.com/mat/trakkor/commits"><img style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;" src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_red_aa0000.png" alt="Fork me on GitHub" /></a>

<script type="text/javascript">

  var _gaq = _gaq || [];
  _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-342605-4']);
  _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);

  (function() {
    var ga = document.createElement('script');
    ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' :
        'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';
    ga.setAttribute('async', 'true');
    document.documentElement.firstChild.appendChild(ga);
  })();

</script>

  <script type="text/javascript">
    jQuery(document).ready(function() {
      jQuery('abbr[class*=timeago]').timeago();
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>


